ZH: 他们正在绞丝机上绞纤维。
EN: They are twisting fibers on the spinning machine.

ZH: 这个机器可以将原材料绞成细丝。
EN: This machine can twist raw materials into fine threads.

ZH: 绞盘上的细绳正在紧绷。
EN: The thin rope on the winch is being tightened.

ZH: 这座桥梁是用绞盘吊起来的。
EN: This bridge was lifted using a winch.

